1293
01:22:17,541 --> 01:22:19,341
- Please stop. Stop!
- Charlie!

1294
01:22:19,343 --> 01:22:21,443
- Mom, there is no reason to go...
- Where is she?

1295
01:22:21,445 --> 01:22:23,547
- Mom, stop!
- Quit it, Otis.

1296
01:22:25,716 --> 01:22:27,183
