to transmit our message.

1301
01:22:40,931 --> 01:22:42,964
- It's close.
- (ELECTRICAL HUMMING)

1302
01:22:42,966 --> 01:22:47,669
Oh. B-127.
I almost forgot.

1303
01:22:47,671 --> 01:22:48,970
I didn't.

1304
01:22:48,972 --> 01:22:50,273
(RAY GUN WHIRS)

1305
01:22:51,175 --> 01:22:52,710
No! Don't shoot!

1306
01:22:54,712 --> 01:22:56,011
(SOBS) No!

1307
01:22:56,013 --> 01:22:58,215
