1310
01:23:19,803 --> 01:23:21,639
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

1311
01:23:23,074 --> 01:23:25,942
I can fix this.
I can fix this.

1312
01:23:25,944 --> 01:23:27,778
(SOBBING)

1313
01:23:30,048 --> 01:23:31,180
Charlie.

1314
01:23:31,182 --> 01:23:34,649
You got to wake up, Bee.
You got to wake up.

1315
01:23:34,651 --> 01:23:35,652
Please.

1316
