1320
01:23:48,900 --> 01:23:50,501
I can fix you.

1321
01:23:53,004 --> 01:23:54,336
Come on, Bee.

1322
01:23:54,338 --> 01:23:55,839
Come back to me.

1323
01:24:02,012 --> 01:24:03,814
Come on, give me
the other one.

1324
01:24:05,149 --> 01:24:06,650
(SNIFFLES)

1325
01:24:10,121 --> 01:24:11,790
Bee, come on.

1326
01:24:13,925 --> 01:24:15,693
I can't lose you, too, Bee.

1327
01:24:16,127 --> 01:24:17,528
Please, Bee!

1328
01:24:20,631 --> 01:24:21,900
(SOBS)

1329
01:24:29,706 --> 01:24:31,041
(CHARLIE SIGHS)

1330
01:24:31,742 --> 01:24:32,744
I'm sorry.

1331
01:24:46,891 --> 01:24:48,026
Oh.

1332
01:24:48,592 --> 01:24:49,760
(SOBS)

1333
01:24:57,735 --> 01:24:59,569
Oh, my God.

1334
01:24:59,571 --> 01:25:01,773
Come on, Bee, we've got
to get you out of here.

1335
01:25:05,677 --> 01:25:07,645
- (VISOR WHIRRING)
- (GASPS)

1336
