- Hang on.

1445
01:31:51,883 --> 01:31:53,819
Oh, my God! Ron!

1446
01:31:55,488 --> 01:31:56,953
(AGENT BURNS GRUNTING)

1447
01:31:56,955 --> 01:31:58,822
Get out of the way!

1448
01:31:58,824 --> 01:32:00,824
Oh, my gosh!
What are you doing?

1449
01:32:00,826 --> 01:32:02,395
