1452
01:32:10,770 --> 01:32:12,839
- (TIRES SQUEAL)
- Whoa!

1453
01:32:14,207 --> 01:32:15,807
(HORN BLARING)

1454
01:32:17,644 --> 01:32:19,176
(HORN BEEPING)

1455
01:32:19,178 --> 01:32:21,078
- (GASPS)
- (BRAKES SCREECH)

1456
01:32:21,080 --> 01:32:22,213
Whoa!

1457
01:32:22,215 --> 01:32:23,882
(BRAKES SCREECH)

1458
01:32:25,618 --> 01:32:26,818
Whoa!

1459
01:32:28,454 --> 01:32:30,022
(ALL SCREAMING)

1460
01:32:34,861 --> 01:32:36,262
Nice driving, Ron.

1461
01:32:38,231 --> 01:32:41,032
(BREATHES HEAVILY)
Is everyone okay?

1462
01:32:41,034 --> 01:32:44,035
Ron! We have
a kid in the car!

1463
01:32:44,037 --> 01:32:46,903
I was trying to save
the other kid! What was I...

1464
01:32:46,905 --> 01:32:48,639
