1465
01:32:48,641 --> 01:32:51,311
Otis? Otis,
are you all right?

1466
01:32:52,712 --> 01:32:56,015
That was radical.

1467
01:33:04,157 --> 01:33:06,025
(TRILLING)

1468
01:33:15,368 --> 01:33:17,936
(ENERGY PULSATING)

