1476
01:34:19,399 --> 01:34:20,933
(VISOR WHIRRING)

1477
01:34:26,539 --> 01:34:29,942
Handle him! And finish
the job this time!

1478
01:34:30,810 --> 01:34:32,179
(HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING)

1479
01:34:41,154 --> 01:34:43,022
(DROPKICK GRUNTING)

1480
01:34:46,559 --> 01:34:47,560
Oh, shit!

1481
01:34:50,831 --> 01:34:52,498
(GRUNTING)

1482
01:35:01,575 --> 01:35:03,477
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1483
01:35:14,922 --> 01:35:16,788
How the hell am I
gonna get up there?

1484
01:35:16,790 --> 01:35:18,991
(CRASHING)

1485
